data.description: **Motivated seller**Ask about an available FHA assumable loan (@4.375%)**Welcome to this one of a kind, custom built home in the heart of Hunters Run. Nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac this 4-bedroom, 4-bathroom house boasts an impressive array of features that will make everyday living a true pleasure. The well-maintained exterior offers a recently updated roof (2016), freshly painted fence and shutters (2023), and professional landscaping. The 2.5 car garage is fully insulated, heated and includes an industrial air compressor, 9’ overhead garage door and 6’ french steel entry doors, making it convenient for any hobbyist. Centered on the first floor is the kitchen where you’ll find stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. French double doors off the back of the kitchen lead to the backyard oasis, where a 16x36 in-ground saltwater pool awaits you. Surrounded by bamboo fencing, this private sanctuary is perfect for summer relaxation and entertaining guests. The large lot spans over half an acre and features a fire pit and a 10x12 storage shed with a full size garage door. The home butts up to Golden Gate Park offering easy access to the community picnic, pee wee football fields, baseball & softball diamonds and the community bike path. A standout feature of this home is the 1080sq/ft finished basement which offers plenty of space including a 5th bedroom and the 4th bathroom. On the second floor you’ll find 4 bedrooms including a master suite with an ensuite bathroom and a spacious walk-in closet. The property is set up with Ring video monitors, keyless entry, smart thermostat and fiber optic high speed internet.This home offers the ideal blend of comfort, convenience, and luxury. Don't miss this opportunity to make it yours. Sellers willing to negotiate up to $6,000 in concessions at closing towards updates.
